(591023, 'Joross Gamboa', '1984-11-28', 131, 'John Ross Sanchez Gamboa (born 28 November 1984) is a Filipino actor. He is best known for his roles in the films Starting Over Again (2014), Deadma Walking (2017), Ang Dalawang Mrs. Reyes (2018), Hello, Love, Goodbye (2019), Rewind (2023).', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/7WGlXF3BVqIELaxiKYRdU7M1iYE.jpg'),
