(928572, 'Scott Eastwood', '1986-03-21', NULL, 'Scott Eastwood (born Scott Clinton Reeves; March 21, 1986) is an American actor, model, and professional skydiver. He has appeared in the films Flags of Our Fathers (2006), Gran Torino (2008), Invictus (2009), The Forger (2012), Trouble with the Curve (2012), Texas Chainsaw (2013), Fury (2014), The Perfect Wave (2014), The Longest Ride (2015), Mercury Plains (2016), Suicide Squad (2016), Snowden (2016) and The Fate of the Furious (2017). He has also been the model for the fragrance Cool Water by Davidoff. He is the youngest son of Academy Award-winning actor-director Clint Eastwood and second youngest of Jacelyn Reeves.\r\n\r\nDescription above from the Wikipedia article Scott Eastwood, licensed under CC-BY-SA, full list of contributors on Wikipedia.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/hBqXeKe2Z7VnAYe7tLTzIvr8po4.jpg'),
(934289, 'Kiernan Shipka', '1999-11-10', NULL, 'Kiernan Brennan Shipka is an American actress. She is known for her roles as Sally Draper in Mad Men and Sabrina Spellman in Chilling Adventures of Sabrina and Riverdale. She also starred in the movies The Blackcoat\'\'s Daughter, Totally Killer, Longlegs & Twisters.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/t2FWVLTIhVRIa398mQAfN4thO5R.jpg'),
(935314, 'Slamet Rahardjo', '1949-01-21', 73, 'Born in 1949, Slamet Rahardjo started his career in theatre. A legendary and highly-regarded Indonesian actor, director, and screenwriter, Rahardjo has received many national and international awards for his work.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/fNDa1QYLuUH8ZpNdbs1os4yX6Xf.jpg'),
(966554, 'Eka Darville', '1989-04-11', 9, '', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/7tNdST92WSTGHmEJbExaRlQHWcW.jpg'),
(970027, 'Marta Hazas', '1977-12-31', 156, 'Marta Hazas (born December 31, 1997)is a Spanish actress born in Santander (Cantabria). She has a degree in jorunalism, and she also studied dramatic arts in Cristina Rota School. She started her career with minor roles in Spanish tv shows like \'\'El comisario\'\', \'\'Hospital central\'\' or \'\'Los hombres de Paco\'\'. Fame came after her role as Amelia in the tv show \'\'El Internado\'\'. Before that, she played other leading roles in shows like \'\'Bandolera\'\' or \'\'Velvet\'\'. She also has been participated in movies like \'\'8 citas\'\' or \'\'Lo contrario al amor\'\'.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/1dbeTFRCbWBt70dIGjYHKVLnpaG.jpg'),
