(1089873, 'Rita Ora', '1990-11-26', NULL, 'Rita Sahatçiu Ora is a British singer-songwriter and actress. Her debut studio album, Ora, debuted at number one in the United Kingdom, and spawned the number-one singles \"R.I.P.\" and \"How We Do\".', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/o1DMrW8vsTYnCcvVTZy6hEvlk4f.jpg'),
(1093919, 'Cecily Strong', '1984-02-08', NULL, 'Cecily Legler Strong (born February 8, 1984) is an American actress and comedian who has been a cast member of Saturday Night Live since 2012. She was born in Springfield, Illinois, and was raised in Oak Park, Illinois, an inner ring suburb of Chicago.She is the daughter of Penelope and William \"Bill\" Strong, who worked as an Associated Press bureau chief and is now managing partner at a Chicago public relations firm.Strong\'\'s parents are divorced.Strong grew up adoring SNL as a child, reenacting sketches with her friend and watching old SNL commercials on VHS. \"I had a tape of the best commercials, and I wore it out, every day.\" She has stated that she was inspired by Phil Hartman.\r\n\r\nShe attended Oak Park and River Forest High School before transferring for her senior year to the Chicago Academy for the Arts, where she graduated in 2002.She then studied acting at California Institute of the Arts (CalArts), graduating in 2006 with a BFA in theatre. After graduating from CalArts, Strong returned to Chicago, where she studied at the Second City Conservatory and iO Chicago.\r\n\r\nDescription above from the Wikipedia article Cecily Strong, licensed under CC-BY-SA, full list of contributors on Wikipedia.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/g1WbsojbgQAB72UfUJnNWPaB4b5.jpg'),
(1100011, 'Slimane Dazi', '1960-05-16', 56, 'Slimane Dazi was born on May 26, 1960, in Nanterre, Hauts-de-Seine, France. He is an actor, known for Only Lovers Left Alive (2013), A Prophet (2009) and Hold Back (2012).', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/tHh9XviWroQWkKOa2jRPh5EkHTW.jpg'),
(1102427, 'Steven Cree', '1981-02-28', 178, 'Steven Cree is a Scottish film, television and theater  actor and writer, known for Outlaw King (2018), Brave (2012) and Outlander (2014). He has been married to Kahleen Crawford since May 29, 2016.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/oH9uSQMJPdFHeVggqvMwheW7nZl.jpg'),
(1104567, 'Maisy Stella', '2003-12-13', 32, 'Maisy Jude Marion Stella is a Canadian singer and actress. She is known for her role as Daphne Conrad on the musical television series Nashville. In 2017, she released her debut solo song, \"Riding Free\", for the soundtrack of the Dreamworks animation series Spirit Riding Free.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/hv01GL5eT8cI7WK73e7XcbAgkPU.jpg'),
