(1185537, 'Fedi Nuril', '1982-07-01', 73, 'Fedrian Nuril is an Indonesian model and actor. He is a part of the Indonesian music band Garasi. Fedi acted in a film of the same name, Garasi (2006), starring with his other band members. The youngest of three, Fedi is mostly known from his role as Fahri in the novel-adapted film Ayat-Ayat Cinta (2008).', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/eKAaZmCglwMb8vjSHhxgE7L9h9S.jpg'),
(1190554, 'Catherine Corcoran', '1992-05-30', NULL, 'She is best known for her staring role in Troma Entertainments, award-winning, \'\'Return to Nuke \'\'Em High\'\' (a revamped, reboot of the 1984 cult classic, \'\'The Class of Nuke \'\'Em High\'\'). Her career also includes roles in Gossip Girl, The Good Wife, MTV Pranks, and working under the mentorship of Academy Award Winning directors Peter Jackson (The Lovely Bones) and Josh Fox (Gasland). She has been featured in various publications including The New York Times, Interview Magazine, TIME Magazine, The Hollywood Reporter and Le Figaro. Much in the vein of her mentors, Catherine is also known for spearheading Troma Entertainments, \'\'Occupy Cannes\'\' Campaign and its subsequent documentary.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/vv3hncIfLPsTj5XonPrMV4UcbPl.jpg'),
(1193391, 'Anthony Gonzalez', '2004-09-23', NULL, 'Young American actor, born in September 23, 2004, son of  Guatemalan immigrants.\r\n\r\nAnthony Gonzalez is know for Imagination of Young (2015),  Icebox (2016), Coco (2017), Prescience (2019) and Blue Miracle (2021).', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/WF7bn6t0LkxwBWyDMWvomVujn7.jpg'),
