(1597365, 'Joseph Quinn', '1994-01-26', 178, 'Joseph Quinn (born January 26, 1994) is an English actor. He is best known for his role as Eddie Munson in the fourth season of the Netflix series Stranger Things (2022) and for his role as Eric in A Quiet Place: Day One (2024). His previous appearances were in the BBC One series Dickensian (2016), Howards End (2017), Les Misérables (2018), and the Sky Atlantic series Catherine the Great (2019).', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/zshhuioZaH8S5ZKdMcojzWi1ntl.jpg'),
