(1643476, 'Yoshino Aoyama', '1996-05-15', 80, 'Yoshino Aoyama (青山 吉能, Aoyama Yoshino, May 15, 1996) is a Japanese voice actress from Kumamoto prefecture. She belongs to 81 Produce.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/18nwTfvgurEelSQqPKbMMtUnKja.jpg'),
