(1675742, 'Mădălina Bellariu Ion', NULL, NULL, 'Mădălina is a Meisner trained actress. She has performed in various stage plays. Her most notable television appearance is \"The Young Pope\", with Jude Law, directed by Paolo Sorrentino. Mădălina plays a pivotal role in the thriller \" Dobaara: See Your Evil\", produced by Relativity Media/B4U Motion Pictures. Mădălina is a polyglot, speaking 5 languages fluently: English, Italian, Romanian, French, Spanish', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/8M8HNOixq1S8YpJUytlIYw72F66.jpg'),
(1676771, 'Samantha Scaffidi', '1989-03-03', NULL, 'Samantha Scaffidi was born as Samantha Nicole Scaffidi. She is an actress and producer, known for Demon Hole (2017), The Grind TV 1.0 (2016) and Terrifier (2016).', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/jwd0XXuc4ibXAXjOxmhsFP0fQEO.jpg'),
