(3524336, 'Abby Fitz', '2001-01-01', 76, 'Abby Fitz is an Irish actress, born in 2001 in Wexford, Ireland. Her full name is Abby May Fitzmaurice. She has been acting since she was 4 years old.\r\n\r\nActing career: Ryan Tubridy\'\'s \"Late Late Toy Show\" advert (2009). Ispcc\'\'s advert and Poster Campaign (2016). Holly Reid, in season 2 of the German TV series \"Der Irland-Krimi\" (2021). Ellie Woods in the Irish horror film \"The Cellar\" (2022). Cara Lockley in the TV Mini Series \"Redemption\" (2022).  Alison in \"Double Blind\" (2022, post-production).\r\n\r\nTraining:  Drama Workshop Programme from the Waterford Youth Arts organisation (WYA).', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/dsIijvByEZr81YGzY7VazWoGheD.jpg'),
