(1092607, 'Benjamin Renner', '1983-11-14', 56, 'Benjamin Renner (born 14 November 1983) is a French cartoonist, animator and filmmaker.  Renner and his fellow producers received a 2014 Academy Awards nomination in the category of Best Animated Feature for the film Ernest & Celestine. He previously directed a short, La queue de la souris (The Mouse\'\'s Tail) in 2008.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/yp4ucXRYU5TdMj16glyoYYoxJcw.jpg');
