(1768215, 'Michael Su', '1967-12-10', 163, 'Michael Su was born on December 10, 1967 in Taipei, Taiwan. He is a cinematographer and director, known for Snow White and the Seven Samurai (2024), Bloodthirst (2023) and Death Count (2022).', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/yNvnLqEHb2FtdB7AW2O0lZelKBO.jpg'),
