(2218465, 'Parker Finn', '1987-03-18', NULL, 'Parker J. Finn (born March 18, 1987) is an American filmmaker. He is best known for directing the horror film Smile (2022). He is the founder of film and television production company Bad Feeling.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/lw1I0voNLS2llYTlDgd6qZzAMZ6.jpg'),
